
<%= f.input(:id, as: :hidden) %>

<br/>
<p class="lead mt-2 mb-4 mx-1">
  This is the last step of the guided registration. Once you proceed, the names
  will be transferred to a validation list. Review that the list is in order and
  don't forget to submit it (at the bottom) for curator review.
</p>

<h3>Names in this guided registration</h3>
<ol class="blockquote">
  <% @tutorial.names.each do |name| %>
    <li><%= link_to_name(name) %></li>
  <% end %>
</ol>

<div class="alert alert-info my-4">
  <h3>Important note</h3>
  <hr/>
  If the effective publication for the names above has already been published in
  a peer-reviewed venue, please continue to <b>Notify about effective
  publication</b> after creating the validation list instead of submitting for
  approval.
</div>


